.entry-header
About Us
Sweetwater Golf & Country Club
A World Of Privilege
Over the years, aggressive capital improvement programs have maintained our status as Orlando’s premier country club.
Contact US
Sweetwater’s stately surroundings, trademark golf course, exquisite cuisine and exceptional service epitomize the country club, raising the bar higher than any other Orlando golf and country club.
Nestled along Wekiva State Park and dotted with timeless elegance, Sweetwater provides a truly memorable experience with each visit. From play on the Tiff-Eagle golf greens to companionship in our dining rooms Sweetwater presents a myriad of social activities for all ages.
We invite you to visit Sweetwater Golf & Country Club – in person or through our website – to discover how you too can unlock a world of endless privileges.

Venue Services - Rising to Every Occasion
Professional services and superior facilities, Sweetwater Golf & Country Club
With our commitment to professional services and superior facilities, Sweetwater Golf & Country Club exemplifies Orlando’s finest venue services. Whether you’re planning an intimate dinner, a grand reception, or a multi-course celebration, our venue specialists will customize an event especially for you and provide both the service and satisfaction to exceed your expectations.
Individually, the country club’s elegant dining rooms (see Banquet Facilities) offer distinctive options for a variety of events – from rehearsal dinners and intimate receptions to private celebrations.
After choosing the venue for your special event, our Specialists will provide you with our list of preferred caterers that have been vetted and tested. It is our club’s guarantee that our preferred caterers will be only the best that Orlando has to offer.
Combined, the clubhouse at Sweetwater Golf & Country Club can accommodate more than 250 guests, making it the ideal venue for any event you can imagine – storybook weddings, bar and bat mitzvahs, anniversary parties, holiday celebrations, corporate events and more.
Additionally, our meticulously landscaped grounds – complete with picturesque fountains and towering trees – can host up to 250 outdoor guests.
To discuss your next event, please contact one of our professional planners at 407.889.4743, ext. 100.

Membership Categories
Membership opportunities here at Sweetwater Golf & Country Club
Contact US
Club members are welcome to reserve any of our venues for private events with a discounted room charge; catering and other details are simply organized with our expert venue staff. (See Venue Services for more information.)
Full Club Membership
Available for families or singles, our Full Club membership entitles you to unlimited access of all Club amenities. You have the option of adding on several attractive enhancements to this membership – Sweetwater Men’s or Women’s Golf Association privileges, USGA handicap service, golf cart trail plan, and more.
Unlimited Golf With Unlimited Cart Membership
Combining unlimited golf play with unlimited cart usage, this membership - for families and singles - is the perfect selection for the avid golfing family. This category not only includes all greens fees and all cart fees, but also allows for the addition of several of the attractive enhancements listed under the Full Club program.
Unlimited Golf Membership
Available for families or singles, our Unlimited Golf membership is just that - unlimited golf with all greens fees included. Providing a terrific value for the fervent golfer, this category allows for the addition of several of the attractive enhancements listed under the Full Club program.
Associate Golf Membership
This introductory program is a perfect fit for the golfer whose schedule allows for just a handful of golf rounds per month. Available for families or singles, this membership saves you 50% off our lowest posted greens fees each time you play. Several of the attractive enhancements listed under the Full Club program may also be added to this category.
Full Fitness Membership
Coming Soon… The Full Fitness Membership will entitle you to enjoy unlimited access to our fitness facility as well as receiving club member benefits such as member events and venue discount rates. Full Fitness Members will also gain access to private locker rooms for the fitness facility.
Contact US
Social Membership
Available for families or singles, our Social Membership entitles you to access all club events and in-club discounts. You may enjoy unlimited dining and are entitled to utilize the Golf Course up to six times per year at discounted rates.
Contact US
*Please contact our Membership Relations Coordinators at 407.889.4743 for current rates, specials and promotions.
Join Membership

Privacy. Pleasure. Privilege
Members of Sweetwater Golf & Country Club experience excellence that exceeds all expectations
Before reviewing our various affordable membership packages and privileges, we encourage you to review our website, become acquainted with the activities and amenities we offer, and discover what we mean when we say, “excellence exceeds expectations at Sweetwater.” Members of Sweetwater Golf & Country Club also enjoy venue service discounts and access to future member-exclusive events.
